This paper deals with video streaming services and Quality of Experience (QoE) for mobile users. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) categories. The use of crowdsourcing and predictive algorithms also suggests that it could belong to the Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) category. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of Android cellphones, which could indicate Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) or Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) categories.
